CUNY-Wide Transgender Day of Remembrance Vigil
college: CUNY School of Labor and Urban Studies
description:
You are invited to our 4th annual CUNY-Wide Transgender Day of Remembrance Vigil. This is a day not only to provide our CUNY community a space to mourn, but we also uplift transgender and nonbinary student voices via our student panel discussion and student art & poetry showcase. 

 

This year’s vigil will be held at the CUNY Graduate Center’s Segal Theater (and over Zoom) on Friday, November 21, 2025 from 4PM - 6PM. Link to RSVP: bit.ly/TDOR25
